WHEREAS, we find it appropriate to acknowledge and applaud the Fayette-Ware Lady
Wildcats for their outstanding season on the hardwood; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE ONE HUNDRED FOURTEENTH
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, that we honor and commend the
members and coaches of the Fayette-Ware Comprehensive High School Lady Wildcats girls'
basketball team upon finishing as runner-up at the 2025 TSSAA Class 3A, District 14
tournament and extend to them our best wishes for every continued success in all their future
endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy.
